location.fullValue: Plan 1 Plan, Upton at Sommers Bend

data.description: New Updated Commission! Upscale family Richmond American 2 story home. Only 2.5 years new. Located in the highly sought-after Master Planned Community of “Sommers Bend” in Temecula Ca. So much attention to detail in this beautiful home. Welcoming veranda porch. All neutral colors to include carpet. Rich vinyl flooring, interior freshly painted. Neat loft. Central heat and air, tankless hot water heater, custom shutters. 3 full bedrooms and 2 full baths. Primary bathroom has a shower and separate sunken tub. Second bathroom has a tub/shower combo. A convenient downstairs powder room as well. Cooks’ kitchen with flashy quartz countertops. Stainless appliances. Adorable covered California room with sitting area in backyard, just freshly landscaped and hardscaped, with drip system. 2 car attached garage with opener. Sommers Bend Master Planned Community offers a stunning clubhouse, fitness center, with resort style pool and separate lap pool. Fitness rooms, BBQ and picnic tables, firepits and a huge 21-acre sports park and miles of trails. Close to shopping, Temecula school district, medical and wineries. 13 Paid for solar panels.
